00:38:39.212 --> 00:38:40.140
complex problem, right?

00:38:40.140 --> 00:38:41.710
Do you start doubting
everything?

00:38:41.710 --> 00:38:44.440
Do you start doubting every
foundational idea that has

00:38:44.440 --> 00:38:46.460
come before it?

00:38:46.460 --> 00:38:48.420
Where do you--

00:38:48.420 --> 00:38:50.700
where is it effective
to doubt?

00:38:50.700 --> 00:38:51.950
Or what is it effective
to doubt?

00:38:55.157 --> 00:38:57.400
Well, you're matching,
