00:47:13.660 --> 00:47:15.110
that's good for you.

00:47:15.110 --> 00:47:17.370
And they sold off their beer
division, they sold off their

00:47:17.370 --> 00:47:18.360
cookies division.

00:47:18.360 --> 00:47:21.340
And now all of us know them as
water, and yogurt, and baby

00:47:21.340 --> 00:47:23.150
food, I think.

00:47:23.150 --> 00:47:25.610
So now they focus on healthy
food that's good.

00:47:25.610 --> 00:47:28.610
Again, these multiple
switches do happen.

00:47:28.610 --> 00:47:32.470
Tends to not be year after
year after year.

00:47:32.470 --> 00:47:34.170
But it's fun when it does.

00:47:37.870 --> 00:47:42.716
AUDIENCE: Reading about Pepsi
and what happened when the CEO

00:47:42.716 --> 00:47:46.612
decided that they wanted
to focus more on

00:47:46.612 --> 00:47:48.070
making healthier products.

00:47:48.070 --> 00:47:50.500
And he tried it for
about a year.

00:47:50.500 --> 00:47:53.497
And then there was a lot of
shareholder push back, and

00:47:53.497 --> 00:47:53.902
they said don't do it.

00:47:53.902 --> 00:47:56.332
And then he had to
switch back.

00:47:56.332 --> 00:47:58.640
I'm asking, was that
the wrong idea?

00:47:58.640 --> 00:48:01.100
Or could he have done it
in a way that worked?

00:48:01.100 --> 00:48:02.730
ALAN INY: I'll give you another
example along those

00:48:02.730 --> 00:48:04.130
lines, as well.

00:48:04.130 --> 00:48:05.620
Because--

00:48:05.620 --> 00:48:07.410
take Netflix.

00:48:07.410 --> 00:48:10.470
In many ways, a fantastic
new box at first.

00:48:10.470 --> 00:48:14.610
Changing, essentially killing
the video store, video rental

00:48:14.610 --> 00:48:18.000
in a store business, and
replacing it with a new box of

00:48:18.000 --> 00:48:19.760
DVD rental by mail.

00:48:19.760 --> 00:48:22.870
OK, new box, 10 years, millions
of subscribers,

00:48:22.870 --> 00:48:24.270
excellent--

00:48:24.270 --> 00:48:25.050
then what happens?

00:48:25.050 --> 00:48:28.150
Just like in the example you
said, they changed a little

00:48:28.150 --> 00:48:31.320
bit too early for their
customers by trying to split

00:48:31.320 --> 00:48:35.270
into two with the streaming
business as well as the mail.

00:48:35.270 --> 00:48:36.350
And there was a huge outcry.

00:48:36.350 --> 00:48:40.680
They lost hundreds of thousands
of subscribers and

00:48:40.680 --> 00:48:43.810
shareholder value and all the
rest, very upsetting.

00:48:43.810 --> 00:48:45.590
They recovered.

00:48:45.590 --> 00:48:48.870
And now, who two years ago
would have predicted that

00:48:48.870 --> 00:48:51.670
Netflix would have award-winning
original

00:48:51.670 --> 00:48:53.050
television programming?

00:48:53.050 --> 00:48:55.820
This is an extraordinary
new box, and

00:48:55.820 --> 00:48:57.890
actually decent stuff.

00:48:57.890 --> 00:49:01.240
And so really again,
continuously reevaluating and

00:49:01.240 --> 00:49:02.840
rethinking some of
these things.

00:49:02.840 --> 00:49:03.900
But you're right.

00:49:03.900 --> 00:49:06.450
The main takeaway from what you
said is that there is a

00:49:06.450 --> 00:49:08.390
right moment for any change.

00:49:08.390 --> 00:49:09.660
And sometimes it'll
be too early.

00:49:09.660 --> 00:49:11.260
Sometimes it'll be too late.

00:49:11.260 --> 00:49:14.160
The most obvious example,
to me, is YouTube.

00:49:14.160 --> 00:49:18.060
If somebody had invented that
a few years earlier there

00:49:18.060 --> 00:49:19.980
would never been enough
bandwidth.

00:49:19.980 --> 00:49:22.150
Nobody had enough bandwidth.

00:49:22.150 --> 00:49:24.770
Not enough people had high speed
internet in their homes,

00:49:24.770 --> 00:49:27.430
is what I'm trying to say, for
it to be very successful.

00:49:27.430 --> 00:49:29.840
And of course, if they had
invented it a few years later,

00:49:29.840 --> 00:49:31.210
someone else would have come
up with something.

00:49:31.210 --> 00:49:32.720
And it would be called
something else.

00:49:32.720 --> 00:49:34.180
So it is a question of timing.

00:49:34.180 --> 00:49:35.170
You're quite right.

00:49:35.170 --> 00:49:39.360
And Netflix, YouTube, and the
example you said are all good

00:49:39.360 --> 00:49:40.810
examples of that.

00:49:40.810 --> 00:49:42.950
It's about what is the right
new box and when?

00:49:46.940 --> 00:49:51.750
Good, well, thank you very
